{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>想要擺脫雜亂無章的習慣追蹤工具，輕鬆培養自律生活嗎？《MyHabitPro》今天限時免費中，它專為那些渴望健身目標、實現正念生活或提升工作效率的你而設計。這款 App 提供簡潔直觀的介面，幫助你毫不費力地維持習慣、保持一致性，是打造理想自我的絕佳夥伴。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-6.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>維持每日習慣連勝</h2>\n    <p>《MyHabitPro》擁有強大連勝系統，每日激勵你堅持習慣。其提供彈性追蹤方式，不論是每週總覽或網格視覺化，皆能清晰呈現進度。搭配詳細數據分析與圖表，助你深入洞察，輕鬆優化個人作息，從此養成自律生活。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-2-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-3-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Habit Tracker – MyHabitPro</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Productivity</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T14:56:50.842266+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":302,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}